TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
What is going on in Luskan?
Do you know anything about cults in the city?
Text: 이 도시에 사교에 대해 아는 게 있나?

TextEng: You knows about cults here, maybe?
Can I ask you some directions?
Me new to city. Need directions.
Text: 나 이 도시에 처음이야. 길 필요해.

TextEng: Is there a place to buy equipment nearby?
Just give me an overview of the area.
Me look for place to sleep.
Me need place to buy stuff.
Actually, I'd rather ask you about something else.
What do you mean? Kurth's? Baram's?
Text: 무슨 뜻이지? 커스 쪽? 바람 쪽?

TextEng: What you mean? Who Kurth? Who Baram?
Text: 무슨 말이야? 커스 누구? 바람 누구?

TextEng: Me not belongs to no one.
Another assault, is it? I'll kill you first!
You want rob me, huh? Me kill you!!
Text: 나 털려는 거지? 내가 너 죽여!!

TextEng: You don't think they rule the city anymore?
Text: 이젠 그들이 도시를 다스리지 않는다고 보는 건가?

TextEng: You thinks they no rule no more?
Text: 이제 걔네가 더는 지배 안 해?

TextEng: Tell me about these High Captains.

Text: 아무도 이 싸움을 멈출 수 없나?

TextEng: What have they done to Luskan?
Text: 그 자들이 러스칸을 어떻게 만들어 놨지?

TextEng: Let me ask you something else.
What manner of creature were you fighting?
